   "source": [
    "# CI/CD Repair RL Agent Training (WS-mode, repo-aligned)\n",
    "### OpenEnv `meta_hackathon` + TRL/GRPO\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook trains a language model agent to debug and repair CI/CD pipelines\n",
    "**using the same workspace-based WebSocket protocol** as `inference.py`\n",
    "(`agent/runner.py::run_task_ws`).\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Environment server**: `cicd_api.py` (FastAPI + WebSocket, port 8001 / HF Space `/api/...`)\n",
    "- **Workspace lifecycle**: `POST /api/workspace/create` (creates a temp workspace,\n",
    "  injects a fault, pre-runs the pipeline → returns `initial_failure_logs`),\n",
    "  then a persistent WebSocket session at `/api/ws/{workspace_id}` carries\n",
    "  `read_file` / `write_file` / `list_files` / `trigger_pipeline` commands.\n",
    "- **Action space (matches `agent/api_client.py::execute_tool`)**:\n",
    "  `read_file`, `write_file`, `list_files`, `trigger_pipeline`,\n",
    "  `set_hypothesis` (local), `finalize` (local).\n",
    "- **Reward shaping**: mirrors `run_task_ws` (read +0.05/-0.02, write +0.10/-0.15,\n",
    "  trigger_pipeline +0.30 pass / +0.05 ok / -0.10 fail, hypothesis ±0.10,\n",
    "  finalize 1.0 if pipeline passed, per-step penalty -0.01).\n",
    "- **System prompt**: re-uses `BASE_SYSTEM_PROMPT_WS` from `agent/prompts.py`.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "### Before you start\n",
    "1. **Runtime → Change runtime type → T4 GPU** (free) or L4/A100 (Pro)\n",
    "2. Have your **Hugging Face token** in Colab Secrets (`HF_TOKEN`)\n",
    "3. Your CI/CD env should be **deployed on HF Spaces** running `cicd_api.py`\n",
    "   (the HF Space root must serve the `/api/*` routes)\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
