    "**Why this notebook matches `inference.py`**\n",
    "- Same workspace-protocol env (`POST /api/workspace/create` -> persistent\n",
    "  `/api/ws/{workspace_id}` WS) as `agent/runner.py::run_task_ws`.\n",
    "- Same action space (`read_file`, `write_file`, `list_files`, `trigger_pipeline`,\n",
    "  `set_hypothesis`, `finalize`) as `agent/api_client.py::execute_tool`.\n",
    "- Same reward shaping (read +0.05/-0.02 pre-trigger, write +0.10/-0.15,\n",
    "  trigger_pipeline +0.30 pass / +0.05 ok / -0.10 fail, hypothesis +/-0.10,\n",
    "  finalize 1.0 if pipeline passed, per-step penalty -0.01).\n",
    "- Same system prompt (`BASE_SYSTEM_PROMPT_WS` from `agent/prompts.py`).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Fault types injected by the env (see `cicd/fault_types.py`)**\n",
    "The HF Space picks one fault per workspace; the agent receives the pre-run\n",
    "failure logs as the incident alert and must read -> hypothesise -> write -> verify -> finalize.\n",
    "\n",
    "**VRAM Guide (T4 = 16 GB)**\n",
    "\n",
